Nonostante le piccole dimensioni,  in grado di

Although its body is small, its proficient
fighting skills enable it to keep up with
big bruisers like Machamp and Hariyama.

Il utilise ses ailes pour contrler avec prcision sa

 parer.

Es nutzt seine Flgel, um sich am Himmel in Position
zu halten. Gegen seine Angriffe aus der Luft kann man
sich nur schwer zur Wehr setzen.

Controla su posicin en el aire con las alas. Lanza

Grazie alle sue ali riesce a controllare con la massima
precisione i movimenti in aria e attacca dallalto,

With its wings, it controls its position in the air.
It likes to attack from above, a maneuver that
is difficult to defend against.
